<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸ”” {{title}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{ownerName}},</p>
        
        <div class="highlight">
            <p><strong>{{text1}}</strong></p>
            <p>Your exchange office "<strong>{{officeName}}</strong>" hasn't updated its exchange rates in the last 24 hours.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>{{text2}}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Why update rates regularly?</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Stay competitive in the market</li>
            <li>Attract more customers</li>
            <li>Improve your office ranking</li>
            <li>Increase visibility on {{app_name}}</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>{{text3}}</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Update Rates Now</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>{{text4}}</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The {{app_name}} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated reminder from {{app_name}}.</p>
        <p>You can manage your notification preferences in your dashboard settings.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
